{"tid":1591473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母「有無人覺得咁多屍係大陸運落黎製造白色恐怖」","createTime":"2019-09-24T07:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T07:29:47.000Z","uid":189595,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8fe40047d12d933ec949ee7c58e80df6df980c","tid":1591473,"uid":189595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"第一<br />\n係一個資訊封閉既社會，殺左人都唔會有問題，點解要運啲屍落香港？製造白色恐怖？如果我係政府會唔會咁撚蠢用呢個方法，我擴大清算既人，見人就拉，比起你擺堆屍有效一萬倍啦。<br />\n第二<br />\n最尾講到中銀，基本上銀行業，尤其中銀既資金係好雄厚，你只可以有限度咁影響佢，我完全唔撚明點解十月一要推中銀而唔推機場，遊行其他行動？因為中央最樂意見到你地搞銀行，因為佢地印銀紙根本唔驚你搞。<br />\n第三，正評數<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>結論：真係好撚柒多鬼帶風向</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3b31677dd2c5a65c21e08753b3cd37cb21206132","tid":1591473,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0bROga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0bROga.jpg&h=5e267a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f589e79e72fb61282f427cd8947f48fbc471a043","tid":1591473,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"殺人係要填命既，贊唔贊成？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1591174/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1591174/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"822abb642dccfc7c5724328e85512ddda581fdc7","tid":1591473,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f589e79e72fb61282f427cd8947f48fbc471a043","tid":1591473,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"殺人係要填命既，贊唔贊成？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1591174/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1591174/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"捉到鬼一隻"},{"pid":"8874c92c22ff595b783ee0e1d60dd435c0165904","tid":1591473,"uid":38548,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"無視晒所有疑點